179
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:52,800
not working, don't double down on it. That bias 
of the sunk cause fallacy really comes into play,  

180
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:56,880
especially when you've poured your heart and 
soul into creating artifacts for marketing.  

181
00:14:56,880 --> 00:15:01,760
So experiment, test, validate. Give people that 
psychological safety to fail, especially your  

182
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:06,480
teams and organizations. And then, yeah, once 
you find what works, really double down on it.

